ristlebane <br>Human Bertoxxulous<br>Dwarf Brell<br>Human Mith Marr<br>Human Karana<br>Human Rodcet Nife<br>Erudite Cazic-Thule<br>Human Innoruuk<br><br>Protection of the Cabbage<br><br>The Star Ruby steins are np since no rare ingredients to farm and selling boatloads of these at 1K each.<br><br>The Golden Idols of Tunare require that bastage Iron Oxide. If you want me to make one of these get me 2K and one iron oxide. <br><br>For those looking for iron oxide there are a few ground spawn in Steamfont on an 8 or 12 or 24 hour timer (no one seems to know for sure) that are gobbled up quick. It also drops rarely off of elementals in Steamfont, Lavastorm, Najena, and The Hole. <br><br>Other Pottery items<br><br>Crucibles of Escape are 3K each<br>WIZ/DRU - recommended level of 20. Effect: Lesser Succor (10.5 casting time), can be clicked from inventory<br><br>I can do other golden idols for other deities but they all require iron oxide too. Any of them are 2K plus an iron oxide plus ask me if I have the imbued gems in stock. I have lots of some (quellious, tunare) and some are so rare or expensive they are unpractical to keep in stock (black sapphires, etc.). If I have the imbued gems in stock no problem if I need them please provide a couple for me or one at a time until I succeed at making it.<br><br>Emerald = Golden Idol of Tunare: <br>AC4 WIS+5 MANA+40 SVD+6 SVP+6<br><br>Amber = Golden Idol of Cazic Thule:<br>AC5 STR+7 WIS+5 INT+5 MANA+30<br><br>Sapphire= Golden Idol of Innoruuk:<br>AC4 INT+5 SvM+9 MANA+40.<br><br>Rose Quartz=Golden Idol of Erollisi Marr:<br>AC8 CHA+5 WIS+5 SvD+9 MANA+40<br><br>Ivory =Golden Idol of Tribunal:<br>Ac5, Wis5, Hp10, Mana40<br><br>Peridot =Golden Idol of Bristlebane:<br>Ac7, Str9, Dx5, Agi5<br><br>Opal =Golden Idol of Rodcet Nife:<br>Ac9, Sta5, Wis5, Mana40<br><br>Plains Pebble =Golden Idol of Karana:<br>4ac 4sta 5wis Mana40<br><br>Ruby= Golden Idol of Brell Serilis:<br>7ac 7str 7sta 4wis<br><br>Diamond = Golden Idol of Mithaniel Marr:<br>9ac 10sta 4wis 30hp<br><br>Fire Opal = Golden Idol of Solusek Ro:<br>4ac 6int 40mana 9svF<br><br>Jade = Golden Idol of Rallos Zek:<br>10ac 9str 5sta 20hp<br><br>Black Pearl = Golden Idol of Prexus:<br>4ac 5int 40mana 9svC<br><br>Topaz = Golden Idol of Quellious<br>6ac 7str 6dex 6agi 20hp<br><br>Black Sapphire = Golden Idol of Bertoxxulous<br>4ac 5wis 5int 40mana 9svD<br><br>BUYING<br>I am buying Iron Oxides for 250pp each. Lots of them. More than you could provide. <br><br>I am also buying Spider silk stacks (50pp each) or Spider silk swatch stacks (100pp each). Also unlimited demand for them. You couldn't provide me enough and don't forsee an end to my demand so you can farm away and be assured I will be there to buy them.<br><br>Also need a ton of acrylia ore. We can arrange a price depending on which pieces you have and quantity.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub114.ezboard.com/ucazanplanewalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cazan Planewalker</A> at: 6/13/02 3:50:00 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#212141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub114.ezboard.com/uplanetium.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Planetium</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.covad.net/~swing4daddy/eyes_066.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/22/02 2:56:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089tradingpost.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=758.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> What does Lesser Succor do, and how much are faithstones? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub114.ezboard.com/ucazanplanewalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cazan Planewalker</A></span><br> <span clas